    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "按周来分三个section：Week 1、Week 2、Week 3。第一周1月1号启动，先做一篇Blog Post，预计两天；同时Social Media运营贯穿整周，五天。",
